+# Advanced C++ Console Chat System - Task 1: Baseline CLI Login/Registration
+
+## Overview
+This is the baseline CLI login/registration layer for the Advanced C++ Console Chat System, implemented in C++17 with SHA-256 password hashing and JSON-based persistence.
+
+## Project Structure
+```
+.
+├── Makefile                    # Build configuration
+├── README.md                   # This file
+├── verify.sh                   # Automated rubric verification script
+├── bin/
+│   └── chat_app               # Compiled executable
+├── data/
+│   └── users.json             # User credentials database
+├── include/
+│   ├── auth.h                 # Authentication interface
+│   └── utils.h                # Utility functions interface
+├── logs/
+│   ├── session_state.json     # Session persistence
+│   └── task1_demo.txt         # Demonstration log
+├── obj/
+│   ├── auth.o                 # Compiled authentication module
