+- `include/friends.hpp` - Friend management interface
+- `src/friends.cpp` - Friend management implementation
+- `data/friends_<username>.json` - Per-user friend data
+- `logs/task2_demo.txt` - Demonstration log
+- `verify_task2.sh` - Automated verification script
+
+### Modified Files
+- `src/main.cpp` - Extended with friend menu and chat mode
+- `Makefile` - Added task2 target
+
+## Data Format
+
+### friends_<username>.json
+```json
+[
+  {"user": "alice", "status": "offline"},
+  {"user": "bob", "status": "offline"}
+]
+```
+
+### List Output Format
